text: Tasty and affordable Indian Muslim food. Self service scoop your own curry gravy from the pot. Great for  people who like their roti drenched in curry!

Very friendly and skillful uncle, even with many customers. One of my favourite places for Maggi Goreng and Prata especially because curries are self-service. Prices are affordable and portion is perfect. Thank you sir.

Very nice ikan bilis fried rice.
Got the wokhey! Generous portions
